  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      History              : Analyzes the origins, contingencies, and outcomes of the American Revolution. Spanning the decades from the 1760s to 1820s, it also seeks to place the Revolution in an Atlantic-wide context and to offer a foundation for studying American institutions.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
