                <h4>The Americas - 400 Level</h4>

    
      
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/hist-403" class="program-course-title">
              HIST 403 History of Quebec Institutions (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-27642" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: History and Classical Studies (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/607">Faculty of Arts</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      History              : Analysis of institutional structures in Quebec with emphasis on the 19th century. Particular attention will be given to legal and property institutions in transition.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
