  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      History              : Developments of China's middle empires, ca. 600-1300 CE.  Studies changing international relations, rapid commercialization, religious developments, the rise of the civil service examination system, and ensuing social change.          </p>

