    <p>
      History              : One large aspect of Cold War, either thematic or regional, will be explored.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Lorenz Luthi (Fall)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
